The draw for the Champions League round of 16 has been conducted. Holders Liverpool has been drawn with Atletico Madrid and Chelsea play Bayern Munich. Real Marid has been paired with Manchester City, while Atalanta takes on Valencia. The first legs will be played on February 18, 19, 25 and 26, with group winners away from home. Second leg ties will be played on March 10, 11, 17 and 18. FULL FIXTURES: Borussia Dortmund vs PSG Real Madrid vs Manchester City Atalanta vs Valencia Atletico Madrid vs Liverpool Chelsea vs Bayern Munich Lyon vs Juventus Tottenham vs RB Leipzig Napoli vs Barcelona Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.